<br>
To be fair, I play a 54 warrior and I've never had difficulty positioning mobs correctly once I gained aggro.  In addition, I have tried to focus on the push various classes (or pets) are creating while they melee and it does not seem to be unmanageable.<br>
<br>
When I send /tells to the main tank about it the usual response I receive is &quot;I guess so...&quot; or &quot;I can try...&quot;  -- just really lackluster and, dare I say it, *lazy* responses.<br>
<br>
My question to you as a community is, is it really that hard to position mobs correctly in the 60+ game?  I'm tempted to run some parses to see how much dps is lost from non-tanks not being behind a mob.  I'd suspect it's quite significant.<br>
<br>
Are warriors (tanks) just ill-informed, or is it very difficult to do?  Are they just lazy, or don't bother because of some other reason? <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=195890" target="top">Aamen Palantir</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Fennin Ro<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em> &quot;Your foes seem endless, their tales unknown.&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=iskandaralazeem>Iskandar Alazeem</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Guardian of the Battlefield</BR>STEEL WARRIOR Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 1160<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/1/03 12:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1949.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: How hard is it (really) to position mobs?</span><hr size=1> No, it's easy. People in general are just lazy. Not just warriors, many classes just bang mobs into the walls without a thought. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=anielact>AnielaCT</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 873<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/1/03 3:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1949.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.fortunecity.com/burnkelethin/picz/banners/aniface.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td>