<br>
To be fair, I play a 54 warrior and I've never had difficulty positioning mobs correctly once I gained aggro. In addition, I have tried to focus on the push various classes (or pets) are creating while they melee and it does not seem to be unmanageable.<br>
<br>
When I send /tells to the main tank about it the usual response I receive is &quot;I guess so...&quot; or &quot;I can try...&quot; -- just really lackluster and, dare I say it, *lazy* responses.<br>
<br>
